Each "detail" should be a DENSE paragraph of 10-20 sentences. It should read like a complete engineering brief — a developer can execute every change from the description alone. Reference specific file paths, function names, prop names, state variables, and CSS classes throughout.

If the project is in great shape (90+), focus suggestions on enhancements: new features, dark mode, localStorage persistence, accessibility, performance optimization.`;

